# JSON Forms Website - Project Architecture

This repository contains the official documentation website for [JSON Forms](https://jsonforms.io), a declarative framework for building JSON-based forms.

## Technology Stack

- **Static Site Generator**: Docusaurus 3.x
- **UI Framework**: React 18 with Material-UI (MUI)
- **Content Format**: MDX (Markdown + JSX)
- **Styling**: Infima CSS framework + Emotion CSS-in-JS
- **Deployment**: Netlify

